div.head: Description of changes for 2011.10
div.p: This is the first public version of this text. It is a first draft primarily created from a comparision of the reims and vatican manuscripts. A provisional apparatus has been created for these manuscripts. Draft transcriptions of the Sorbonne and St. Victor manuscripts. Corrections and additions will be made after a collation comparision of all available manuscript witnesses. Citations and cross-references still need to be added."
